{"tid":46432,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":" [I/A]NHN x niconico #COMPAS","createTime":"2016-12-19T15:57:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T17:20:57.000Z","uid":49995,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"78eb47ce15955f24fe3e10c787c52fc8a700cb27","tid":46432,"uid":49995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T15:57:43.000Z","msg":"＃COMPAS ～戰鬥神意解析系統～<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/AAtZXSj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAAtZXSj.jpg&h=32e326d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本作是由 NHN PlayArt 與 DWANGO 聯手打造的合作企畫專案作品，是一款三對三的即時對戰遊戲。在短短三分鐘的戰鬥時間當中，濃縮了組合技能卡片來編輯牌庫、動作遊戲系統，以及戰略遊戲等眾多不<br />\n同要素。<br />\n<br />\n本專案企畫是由 NHN PlayArt 負責開發遊戲系統並經營遊戲，而 DWANGO 則是負責讓在同公司經營的影片投稿網站「niconico」上活動的眾多創作者一起製作各種智財產品，以及搭載 niconico 智慧型手機開發套件等等，希望可以發揮兩間公司各自長處，同時進行遊戲企畫開發、各種設計、製作音樂，甚至是遊戲實況等活動。<br />\n<br />\n而 iOS/Android 遊戲軟體《＃COMPAS～戰鬥神意解析系統～》則是一款採用「單場戰鬥三分鐘」，要和同伴組成隊伍、與其他玩家的隊伍來場三對三戰鬥，目標是爭奪配置在關卡上的據點等基本規則的即時制對戰遊戲。玩家還可以收集各種不同的技能卡片，編輯出能對應各種不同戰略的最強牌庫，準備迎接更多場對戰。在一場三分鐘的戰鬥當中，濃縮了動作遊戲、戰略遊戲和卡片遊戲要素，可以說是一款全新類型的對戰遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n巴哈:<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/7/139447.html#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2F7%2F139447.html%23&d=gXHq9wDoENUYm84wbPOUYXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=7aa55add\" target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/7/139447.html#</a><br />\n影片介紹:<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_dWUdeWdL-k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_dWUdeWdL-k&d=gXHq9wDoENUYm84wbPOUYXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=697548f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_dWUdeWdL-k</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/vuVXlI4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FvuVXlI4.jpg&h=8f04b8e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n集合眾多在 niconico 活躍的創作者<br />\n <br />\n　　本作將會邀請眾多在 niconico 網站上活躍的畫家、VOCALOID P 來負責製作會在遊戲當中登場的角色設計、卡片牌面以及角色主題曲等等內容。而且還請到豪華配音員陣容負責配音，將會看到充滿魅力的 3D 角色在遊戲場地當中出現。<br />\n <br />\n<strong>VOCALOID P</strong>：&amp;#12363;&amp;#12356;&amp;#12426;&amp;#12365;&amp;#12505;&amp;#12450;、&amp;#12480;&amp;#12523;&amp;#12499;&amp;#12483;&amp;#12471;&amp;#12517;P、&amp;#12490;&amp;#12518;&amp;#12479;&amp;#12531;星人、buzzG、164、&amp;#12509;&amp;#12522;&amp;#12473;&amp;#12500;&amp;#12459;&amp;#12487;&amp;#12522;&amp;#12540;、PolyphonicBranch、&amp;#12414;&amp;#12405;&amp;#12414;&amp;#12405;、MARETU、40mP<br />\n<br />\n<strong>畫家</strong>：秋赤音、M.B、&amp;#12362;&amp;#12416;&amp;#12383;&amp;#12388;、&amp;#12371;&amp;#12415;&amp;#12397;、鈴&amp;#12494;助、&amp;#12383;&amp;#12414;、&amp;#12385;&amp;#12419;&amp;#12418;&amp;#12540;&amp;#12356;、No.734、&amp;#12412;&amp;#12354;&amp;#12429;、U井T吾、&amp;#12426;&amp;#12421;&amp;#12358;&amp;#12379;&amp;#12540;、六羽田&amp;#12488;&amp;#12514;&amp;#12456;"},{"pid":"a4427a08521f717c8a92a9c8cf81a48acaca941f","tid":46432,"uid":49995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:00:30.000Z","msg":"VOCALOID P：かいりきベア、ダルビッシュP、ナユタン星人、buzzG、164、ポリスピカデリー、PolyphonicBranch、まふまふ、MARETU、40mP<br />\n<br />\n畫家：秋赤音、M.B、おむたつ、こみね、鈴ノ助、たま、ちゃもーい、No.734、ぼあろ、U井T吾、りゅうせー、六羽田トモエ"},{"pid":"973482ad295defbdcd645b9ca5a529283650cc69","tid":46432,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:40:28.000Z","msg":"玩法幾正，留名"},{"pid":"060c898c19226462c0d17a9cd9a260660358b316","tid":46432,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:48:40.000Z","msg":"一場3分鐘部機熱到爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4886a409ea700600f25a4550571e9d4a58cf42","tid":46432,"uid":49995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:17:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一場3分鐘部機熱到爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 應該同白猫一樣命運變ios限定<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfcdb6b908007d22f5d6ecbd774a38f43cd03f32","tid":46432,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:52:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一場3分鐘部機熱到爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 應該同白猫一樣命運變ios限定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得用手機玩真係好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一邊要向唔同方向行,一邊要望住周圍<br />\n仲要出卡,睇對面屬性轉屬性,睇地圖,cap點<br />\n咁細嘅mon 要同時又touch screen又睇咁多野真係好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n整做webgame 用電腦玩可能仲適合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d40e23e25075db9a318b8a520289d7a294a827","tid":46432,"uid":14404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:55:53.000Z","msg":"d卡原來跟rank逐層開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開波冇留意抽晒d石仲諗點解黎黎去去都係嗰幾張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff94eda128e2de93cb6e5287f9435da3d7b7bae5","tid":46432,"uid":14404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T18:03:25.000Z","msg":"d bgm好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nV家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba47a5f3c2f0871621baeeb5dc3b182f67d4555d","tid":46432,"uid":27488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T19:36:27.000Z","msg":"有玩法介紹 睇唔明"},{"pid":"d63a0b163a36d9c3bfd91a763a0751c223ce3c85","tid":46432,"uid":49995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T01:52:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一場3分鐘部機熱到爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 應該同白猫一樣命運變ios限定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得用手機玩真係好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一邊要向唔同方向行,一邊要望住周圍<br />\n仲要出卡,睇對面屬性轉屬性,睇地圖,cap點<br />\n咁細嘅mon 要同時又touch screen又睇咁多野真係好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n整做webgame 用電腦玩可能仲適合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係 電話玩兩場就del左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n轉落ipad度玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a0a02f67c29a15bcbfbed64ea4109501b79331","tid":46432,"uid":49995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T01:55:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>d bgm好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nV家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係因為V家先入坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nicovideo.jp/watch/sm30228596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nicovideo.jp%2Fwatch%2Fsm30228596&d=gXHq9wDoENUYm84wbPOUYXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=8f731131\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nicovideo.jp/watch/sm30228596</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nicovideo.jp/watch/sm30105817?ref=video%2Franking%2Ffav%2Fdaily%2Fvocaloid%2Fnow%2F22\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nicovideo.jp%2Fwatch%2Fsm30105817%3Fref%3Dvideo%252Franking%252Ffav%252Fdaily%252Fvocaloid%252Fnow%252F22&d=gXHq9wDoENUYm84wbPOUYXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=3a421b98\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nicovideo.jp/watch/sm30105817?ref=video%2Franking%2Ffav%2Fdaily%2Fvocaloid%2Fnow%2F22</a>"},{"pid":"9c2c12d47715e37aaf109a06a17b944625b8efbc","tid":46432,"uid":49995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T02:00:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有玩法介紹 睇唔明</blockquote><br />\n隻game岩岩出 巴哈o個邊都冇乜資料<br />\n基本上過左教學再實戰一兩場就會ok識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db39f38375c9783d880a66c9de0f4ca1656c4c6","tid":46432,"uid":14404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T02:23:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有玩法介紹 睇唔明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當敵人係攻擊範圍就會自動攻擊<br />\n撳實平時就係蓄力技，對敵方塔就可以加速佔領(好似係)<br />\n將卡上推係出技，下拉係將角色變成嗰張卡嘅屬性(典型嘅火水草互剋)<br />\n角色儲滿氣上推係開大技<br />\n限時內最多塔嗰隊贏/其中一隊佔晒5座塔就會直接勝利"},{"pid":"babfc5c6cea3f7509179e6b3b1bf995ebd38e7a8","tid":46432,"uid":66839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T00:27:21.000Z","msg":"好難上rank D"},{"pid":"b8a9beb6acd357cdd516ec74bbb04e74b2ed0b75","tid":46432,"uid":14404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T03:43:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好難上rank D</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲要輸左咩獎勵都冇真係好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2de83b41cef2a20d7427f37a1a374a481f3502d","tid":46432,"uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T04:52:42.000Z","msg":"好似幾好玩"},{"pid":"e6bd8e1145b715cd30b7fd866167b36e5b51c18b","tid":46432,"uid":37763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T13:42:15.000Z","msg":"抽野應該抽邊部？"},{"pid":"381acdff597ac99f967ee7cbb707b228c15dbfe8","tid":46432,"uid":14404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:20:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抽野應該抽邊部？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第一部係抽卡<br />\n卡嘅種類會跟你嘅rank開放<br />\n啫係越高rank越多卡抽<br />\n至於咩rank有咩卡可以去返「備」到睇，一目了然<br />\n唔建議低rank all-in晒佢，因為會抽黎抽去都係嗰幾張<br />\n抽到基本野打到rank D再抽都唔遲<br />\n第二部係課金抽<br />\n第三部每星期一次免費11連<br />\n第四部就每4個鐘一免費抽<br />\n第二頁就抽角<br />\n係「勇」可以睇晒有咩角<br />\n冇話邊隻特別勁，睇你喜好<br />\n升lv會送卷，有就抽晒佢啦<br />\n重複角會開skin同角色專用強化石"},{"pid":"fd8a59f69bf323ea657f39143f85c2632db3cce9","tid":46432,"uid":1390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:38:23.000Z","msg":"暫時都係遠攻角色有優勢"},{"pid":"8fb58f1970b4d0c469e59f28a4339954c711ac27","tid":46432,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:24:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>暫時都係遠攻角色有優勢</blockquote><br />\n我覺得識玩最勁係果隻機械女...<br />\n<br />\n跑得快過小明周街cap 點,然後又可以開大技送晒對面返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對到識玩真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3948da7855317da19aa41d1b0330ade7e2e54936","tid":46432,"uid":14404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:46:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>暫時都係遠攻角色有優勢</blockquote><br />\n我覺得識玩最勁係果隻機械女...<br />\n<br />\n跑得快過小明周街cap 點,然後又可以開大技送晒對面返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對到識玩真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/014429_80eda803c5da33c78d2ea5748bb7689f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F014429_80eda803c5da33c78d2ea5748bb7689f.jpg&h=c4361d09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事實證明速度角勝率最高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590084f40f0f0dd380b18f2cc8237568c7621be3","tid":46432,"uid":47200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T18:49:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/014429_80eda803c5da33c78d2ea5748bb7689f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F014429_80eda803c5da33c78d2ea5748bb7689f.jpg&h=c4361d09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事實證明速度角勝率最高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n魔法少女真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n電鋸女勁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n識打玩剋屬可以好高攻<br />\n盾女守點好麻煩打不死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3ac5ca3257425e020a8ea4d5c7e32b8e9b38f4","tid":46432,"uid":49995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:41:10.000Z","msg":"要行到近一近先知對面咩屬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e33a9177f6c631c01d52a657d95cf6b01a8124","tid":46432,"uid":47320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:32:05.000Z","msg":"想問下隻game個會員有咩優惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee192ea3dabbea97906530135c95fc50ace8bc39","tid":46432,"uid":49995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T15:29:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下隻game個會員有咩優惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n升人lv會多一樣會員獎勵<br />\n抽卡既E罐量會多d<br />\n暫時知既係咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}